### Download Trinity 
$ wget https://github.com/trinityrnaseq/trinityseq/releases/download/Trinity-v2.15.1/trinityrnaseq-v2.15.1.FULL.tar.gz
### unzip
$ tar xfvz trinityrnaseq-v2.15.1.FULL.tar.gz
$ cd trinityrnaseq-v2.15.1/
$ make

